==Results==
*[[1994 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1994]]: '''quarterfinalists'''
*[[1996 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1996]]: third in qualifying group
*[[1998 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1998]]: '''quarter finals'''
*[[2000 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2000]]: second in qualifying group, lost in qualification play-off
*[[2002 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2002]]: second in qualifying group
*[[2004 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2004]]: second in qualifying group
*[[2006 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2006]]: second in qualifying group, lost in qualification play-off
*[[2007 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2007]]: lost in qualification play-off
*[[2009 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2009]]: second in qualifying group

